<li id="cite_note-54"><b><a href="#cite_ref-54" title="">^</a></b> Wexler, <i>Emma Goldman in Exile</i>, pp. 193–194.</li>
<li id="cite_note-55"><b><a href="#cite_ref-55" title="">^</a></b> Newell, p. xiii.</li>
<li id="cite_note-56"><b><a href="#cite_ref-56" title="">^</a></b> Goldman, "Preface", p. xi.</li>
</ol>
