<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFDrinnon1975">Drinnon, Richard and Anna Maria, eds. (1975). <i>Nowhere at Home: Letters from Exile of Emma Goldman and Alexander Berkman</i>. New York: Schocken Books. <a href="/wiki/OCLC" title="OCLC" class="mw-redirect">OCLC</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/oclc/1055309" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/oclc/1055309" rel="nofollow">1055309</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Nowhere+at+Home%3A+Letters+from+Exile+of+Emma+Goldman+and+Alexander+Berkman&amp;rft.aulast=Drinnon&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard+and+Anna+Maria%2C+eds.&amp;rft.au=Drinnon%2C+Richard+and+Anna+Maria%2C+eds.&amp;rft.date=1975&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Schocken+Books&amp;rft_id=info:oclcnum/1055309&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Alexander_Berkman"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book"><i><a href="http://www.archive.org/details/fragmentofprison00gold" class="external text" title="http://www.archive.org/details/fragmentofprison00gold" rel="nofollow">A Fragment of the Prison Experiences of Emma Goldman and Alexander Berkman</a></i>. New York: Stella Comyn. 1919. <a href="/wiki/OCLC" title="OCLC" class="mw-redirect">OCLC</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/oclc/26957788" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/oclc/26957788" rel="nofollow">26957788</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.archive.org/details/fragmentofprison00gold" class="external free" title="http://www.archive.org/details/fragmentofprison00gold" rel="nofollow">http://www.archive.org/details/fragmentofprison00gold</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+Fragment+of+the+Prison+Experiences+of+Emma+Goldman+and+Alexander+Berkman&amp;rft.date=1919&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Stella+Comyn&amp;rft_id=info:oclcnum/26957788&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.archive.org%2Fdetails%2Ffragmentofprison00gold&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Alexander_Berkman"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
